{"tid":621876,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)明日之後 顫慄異次元 新羅拉","createTime":"2018-04-08T16:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T18:21:40.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a25ee6120c44b38eaa968cf1a8d3bf7e71f41640","tid":621876,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=SYqxIXBzcL4VdvXwcwyTEVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=ab530ad0\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=SYqxIXBzcL4VdvXwcwyTEVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=3d6c4749\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/58/The_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F58%2FThe_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg&h=bc58c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3d/Pandorum-Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3d%2FPandorum-Poster.jpg&h=a3bcdf0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5f/Tomb_Raider_official_teaser_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5f%2FTomb_Raider_official_teaser_poster.jpg&h=6b1a7b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在一片已經極度融化的南極冰川上，古氣候學家傑克&middot;霍爾與同事弗蘭克和傑森在冰川上考察時，親眼目睹整個拉森冰架全部斷裂。傑克隨後將有關全球暖化調查結果，在新德里舉行的聯合國研討會上作出報告，聲明兩極冰川融化已經阻斷了北大西洋洋流的暖洋流，而這種情況繼續持續下去將會在未來形成另一個冰河時期。但參加會議的各國元首對此感到荒謬，美國副總統雷蒙&middot;貝克甚至把傑克的理論當作笑話看待。傑克回到華盛頓後致電自己的妻子露西，得知自己兒子山姆即將去紐約參加科學知識競賽<br />\n<br />\n2.近兩百年後地球人口爆炸，滿載人類希望，冷凍睡眠航向外太空的新樂土。隨著船艙裡航員紛紛甦醒，從深度睡眠而凌亂斷裂的記憶，逐漸拼湊自己的身分和此航的目的，同時不明攻擊事件讓他們發現，船上似乎有著意料外的東西.......<br />\n<br />\n3.在蘿拉&middot;卡芙特的父親理查&middot;卡芙特失蹤後，蘿拉靠騎單車送外賣為生，在她出車禍並被帶到警局後，里查德在商業上的夥伴安娜保釋了她，並警告她若不繼承里查德的遺產，那些財產可能會被賣掉。在蘿拉不情願地接受後，她發現一則來自里查的訊息，得知他失蹤前正在調查邪馬台女王卑彌呼。里查要求蘿拉燒掉研究，但蘿拉沒有這麼做，反而踏上尋找父親的旅途<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=SYqxIXBzcL4VdvXwcwyTEVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4e8247dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=SYqxIXBzcL4VdvXwcwyTEVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=f8bb3d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d20887dc8d474caf3b3805e081e10aa3fc03f60","tid":621876,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96433a091998458bdb89e5bba3fcc0309fbd1684","tid":621876,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a